    "Gap-Fill Question SASentiment Analysis TS Text summarization REVIEW PROCESSThere are numerous studies on named entity recognition that are available in the existing literature.",
    "To select the most effective NER method, it cannot be easy to manually search through the popular databases for research articles.",
    "Therefore, a methodology is required to evaluate the majority of research on NER in order to find out about innovative approaches.",
    "The novel review process discussed in three steps, as explained below.Step I: Research questions and its motivationIn this phase, we have given the four RQs and its motivation, as represent in Table 2.",
